EInvesting%20mogul%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fray-dalio-warning-capitalism-american-dream-inequality-economics-billionaire-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERay%20Dalio%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20tariffs%20aren't%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20tax%20revenue%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20also%20a%20way%20for%20countries%20to%20prepare%20their%20economies%20for%20times%20of%20conflict%20and%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Trump%20administration%20announced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-liberation-day-reciprocal-tariffs-speech-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereciprocal%20tariffs%20on%20China%2C%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20and%20dozens%20of%20other%20regions%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Dalio%20wrote%20in%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%20that%20import%20taxes%20were%20%26quot%3Bnecessary%20in%20times%20of%20an%20international%20great%20power%20conflict.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20billionaire's%20reason%3F%20They%20tend%20to%20lower%20reliance%20on%20foreign%20supply%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fray-dalio-indonesia-sovereign-wealth-fund-advisor-danantara-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDalio%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20founded%20the%20hedge%20fund%20Bridgewater%20Associates%2C%20wrote%20that%20the%20tariffs%20%26quot%3Bcan%20reduce%20both%20current%20account%20and%20capital%20account%20imbalances.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhich%2C%20in%20plain%20English%2C%20means%20reducing%20the%20dependencies%20on%20foreign%20production%20and%20foreign%20capital%2C%20which%20is%20especially%20valued%20in%20times%20of%20global%20geopolitical%20conflicts%20or%20wars%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20billionaire%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20wrote%20that%20this%20makes%20local%20companies%20less%20efficient%20because%20global%20supply%20chains%20are%20stifled%20but%20more%20survivable%20as%20long%20as%20domestic%20consumers%20can%20still%20buy%20enough%20of%20their%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDalio's%20post%20wasn't%20specifically%20dissecting%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-futures-trump-liberation-day-tariffs-apple-nike-amazon-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20administration's%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20he's%20not%20necessarily%20saying%20that%20the%20White%20House%20introduced%20these%20taxes%20in%20expectation%20of%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%2C%20he%20wrote%20about%20tariffs%20in%20general%2C%20highlighting%20their%20typical%20effects%20and%20the%20potential%20motivations%20for%20governments%20to%20introduce%20such%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20billionaire%20wrote%20that%20tariffs%20tend%20to%20bring%20inflation%20to%20the%20countries%20that%20introduce%20them%20and%20stagflation%20to%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Dalio's%20point%20about%20a%20potential%20%26quot%3Binternational%20great%20power%20conflict%26quot%3B%20aligns%20with%20the%20billionaire's%20regular%20warnings%20that%20the%20world%20is%20moving%20toward%20a%20period%20of%20great%20strife%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-forgot-how-to-fight-real-war-veteran-in-ukraine-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20risk%20of%20war%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20billionaire%20published%20a%20book%20about%20this%20belief%20in%202021%2C%20in%20which%20he%20predicted%20that%20US-China%20competition%20would%20bring%20fundamental%2C%20messy%20changes%20to%20how%20the%20world%20is%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227d24b7a8-2354-4cb4-9129-35784871ee0c%5C%22%3EEither%20way%2C%20US%20debt%20must%20be%20tackled%2C%20Dalio%20says%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20post%20on%20Wednesday%20about%20tariffs%2C%20Dalio%20recalled%20another%20of%20his%20usual%20points%20about%20the%20state%20of%20the%20world%3A%20He%20believes%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fray-dalio-frank-d