20tell%20them%20to%20watch%20two%20balls%3A%20one%20green%20and%20one%20red.%20Then%2C%20we%20tell%20them%20which%20ball%20to%20catch.%20If%20their%20reaction%20speed%20is%20slower%20than%20half%20a%20second%2C%20it%20is%20not%20fast%20enough.%20This%20is%20the%20top%20requirement%20for%20all%20pilots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFine%20motor%20skills%20are%20also%20very%20important%20because%20the%20drone%20controls%20are%20sensitive.%20If%20one%20of%20our%20candidates%20works%20with%20a%20hammer%20in%20their%20day%20job%2C%20they%20may%20be%20good%20at%20big%20movements%2C%20but%20it%20may%20be%20hard%20for%20them%20to%20be%20a%20drone%20pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20they%20play%20the%20piano%20or%20a%20similar%20instrument%2C%20they%20will%20usually%20learn%20fast.%20Knowing%20how%20to%20play%20music%20is%20a%20strong%20sign%20you%20will%20be%20a%20successful%20drone%20pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20good%20with%20music%2C%20your%20brain%20has%20to%20be%20wired%20to%20think%20ahead.%20You%20have%20to%20multitask%20and%20plan%20your%20next%20steps%20while%20you%20are%20already%20using%20your%20fingers%20for%20finer%20movements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20know%20how%20to%20think%20ahead%2C%20your%20choices%20will%20be%20made%20with%20foresight.%20Those%20choices%20matter%20when%20you%20fly%20in%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Drone%20Fight%20Club%20staff%20carry%20out%20outdoor%20training%20at%20a%20range%20in%20Ukraine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eb8f8069253ccddf9ad6c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22963%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBasic%20courses%20at%20Drone%20Fight%20Club%20last%20a%20minimum%20of%20three%20weeks.%3Cp%3EDrone%20Fight%20Club%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWomen%20who%20excel%20at%20sewing%20are%20also%20often%20great%20combat%20drone%20pilots.%20Here%2C%20it's%20the%20same.%20They%20need%20to%20think%20ahead%20to%20envision%20