that%20bring%20foreign%20goods%20into%20the%20country%20pay%20taxes%20or%20tariffs%20to%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20you%20will%20not%20have%20to%20pay%20the%20tariff%20directly%2C%20the%20company%20can%20decide%20to%20increase%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20product%20to%20compensate%20for%20the%20tariff%20amount%2C%20which%20means%20you%2C%20as%20a%20consumer%2C%20might%20end%20up%20paying%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETariffs%20make%20foreign%20products%20costlier%20and%20harder%20to%20sell%20abroad.%20Foreign%20companies%20might%20have%20to%20cut%20prices%20and%20sacrifice%20profits%20to%20offset%20the%20tariff%20and%20retain%20their%20market%20share%20in%20the%20respective%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5%20items%20likely%20to%20be%20expensive%20for%20Americans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECars%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump%20has%20announced%20a%20flat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-tariffs-25-tariff-automotive-industry-impact-ndtv-explains-impact-on-india-8022347%5C%22%3E25%20per%20cent%20tariff%20on%20cars%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20parts.%20This%20means%20the%20cost%20of%20cars%20built%20in%20America%20will%20increase%20along%20with%20those%20imported%20into%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20tariffs%20aim%20to%20boost%20US%20manufacturing%2C%20automobiles%20built%20in%20US%20factories%20will%20still%20take%20a%20hit%20as%20taxes%20will%20be%20levied%20on%20parts%20as%20well.%20All%2010.2%20million%20cars%20built%20in%20US%20factories%20last%20year%20were%20built%20with%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20imported%20parts%2C%20mainly%20from%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%2C%20reported%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2025%2F03%2F27%2Fcars%2Fauto-tariffs-car-prices-impact-hnk-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoind