oing%20to%20fight%20these%20tariffs%20with%20counter%20measures%2C%26quot%3B%20Carney%20said%20in%20Ottawa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBritish%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%2C%20who%20made%20intense%20comments%2C%20said%20a%20%26quot%3Btrade%20war%20is%20in%20nobody's%20interests.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20prepared%20for%20all%20eventualities%20--%20and%20we%20will%20rule%20nothing%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGermany%20warned%20that%20trade%20wars%20hurt%20%26quot%3Bboth%20sides.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-unveils-reciprocal-tariffs-on-countries-see-full-list-liberation-day-tariffs-donald-trump-8073189%5C%22%3E%C2%A0Trump%20Unveils%20Reciprocal%20Tariffs%20On%20Countries.%20See%20Full%20List%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpanish%20Prime%20Minister%20Pedro%20Sanchez%20said%20his%20country%20would%20%26quot%3Bprotect%20its%20companies%20and%20workers%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20committed%20to%20an%20open%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESweden%20Prime%20Minister%20Ulf%20Kristersson%20noted%20that%20his%20nation%20doesn't%20want%20growing%20trade%20barriers.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20want%20a%20trade%20war%20...%20We%20want%20to%20find%20our%20way%20back%20to%20a%20path%20of%20trade%20and%20cooperation%20together%20with%20the%20US%2C%20so%20that%20people%20in%20our%20countries%20can%20enjoy%20a%20better%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIrish%20Trade%20Minister%20Simon%20Harris%20said%20Ireland%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20(EU)%20were%20ready%20to%20find%20a%20negotiated%20solution%20with%20the%20US.%20%26quot%3BNegotiation%20and%20dialogue%20are%20always%20the%20best%20way%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EItalian%20Prime%20Minister%20Giorgia%20Meloni%2C%20a%20Trump%20ally%2C%20also%20vowed%20to%20work%20with%20President%20Trump%20to%20find%20an%20agreement%20to%20avoid%20the%20%26quot%3Btrade%20war%20that%20would%20inevitably%20weaken%20the%20West%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20do%20everything%20we%20can%20to%20work%20towards%20an%20agreement%20with%20the%20United%20States%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20avoiding%20a%20trade%20war%20that%20would%20inevitably%20weaken%20the%20West%20in%20favor%20of%20other%20global%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20Union%20will%20react%20to%20new%20Trump%20tariffs%20%26quot%3Bbefore%20the%20end%20of%20April%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20French%20government%20spokeswoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2027-nation%20bloc's%20initial%20salvo%20would%20counter%20US%20actions%20on%20steel%20and%20aluminum%2C%20followed%20by%20sector-by-sector%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20commerce%20ministry%20called%20for%20Washington%20to%20%26quot%3Bimmediately%20cancel%26quot%3B%20sweeping%20new%20tariffs%2C%20warning%20they%20%26quot%3Bendanger%20global%20economic%20development%26quot%3B%20and%20would%20hurt%20US%20interests%20and%20international%20supply%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20urges%20the%20US%20to%20immediately%20cancel%20unilateral%20tariff%20measures%20and%20properly%20resolve%20differences%20with%20trade%20partners%20through%20equal%20dialogue%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20winner%20in%20a%20trade%20war%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20way%20out%20for%20protectionism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Latin%20America's%20biggest%20economy%2C%20Brazil%2C%20approved%20a%20law%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20counter%20the%2010%20per%20cent%20tariff%20imposed%20by%20Trump.%20There%20was%20no%20immediate%20reaction%20from%20the%20president%2C%20but%20last%20week%2C%20Luiz%20Inacio%20Lula%20da%20Silva%20said%20his%20country%20%26quot%3Bcannot%20stand%20still%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22pu