tralian%20blue-chip%20stocks%20opened%20in%20the%20red%20on%20Thursday%2C%20as%20one%20of%20the%20first%20global%20markets%20reacted%20to%20the%20development.%20Asia's%20markets%20were%20also%20set%20to%20slide%20as%20the%20bigger-than-expected%20wall%20of%20taxes%20was%20imposed%20around%20the%20world's%20largest%20economy%2C%20upending%20trade%20and%20supply%20chains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EStocks%20Take%20A%20Dive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENasdaq%20futures%20slipped%204%20per%20cent%2C%20with%20tech%20on%20the%20front%20line%20after%20China%2C%20a%20significant%20manufacturing%20hub%2C%20was%20hit%20with%20a%2034%20per%20cent%20levy%20on%20top%20of%20a%20previous%2020%20per%20cent%20tariff.%20Apple%20shares%20were%20down%20nearly%207%20per%20cent%20in%20after-hours%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%20futures%20tumbled%203.3%20per%20cent%20and%20Nikkei%20futures%20dropped%20more%20than%204%20per%20cent.%20The%20US%20dollar%20was%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20higher%20in%20rollercoaster%20currency%20trade%2C%20except%20against%20the%20safe-haven%20yen%2C%20which%20surged%20to%20148.15%20per%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralian%20blue-chip%20stocks%20dipped%20nearly%20two%20percent.%20A%20benchmark%20index%20of%20the%20country's%20largest%20200%20listed%20companies%20dropped%201.96%20percent%2020%20minutes%20after%20opening%2C%20as%20traders%20came%20to%20grips%20with%2010%20percent%20US%20tariffs%20on%20Australian%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20energy%20and%20financial%20services%20sectors%20were%20among%20the%20hardest%20hit%20on%20the%20ASX200%20index%2C%20shedding%20more%20than%20two%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20conference%20announcing%20the%20global%20tariffs%2C%20Trump%20singled%20out%20Australia's%20beef%20industry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETokyo's%20key%20Nikkei%20index%20fell%20more%20than%20three%20percent%20at%20the%20open%20on%20Thursday%20after%20Trump%20imposed%2024%20per%20cent%20tariffs%20on%20Japan.%20The%20benchmark%20Nikkei%20225%20index%20was%20down%203.42%20percent%2C%20or%201%2C222.77%20points%2C%20at%2034%2C503.10%20in%20early%20trade%2C%20while%20the%20broader%20Topix%20index%20was%20down%203.32%20percent%2C%20or%2087.93%20points%2C%20at%202%2C562.36.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVan%20Eck's%20Vietnam%20ETF%20also%20fell%20more%20than%208%20per%20cent%20in%20after-hours%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGold%20Hits%20New%20Record%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOil%20prices%20dropped%20%242%20on%20Thursday%20after%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20announced%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20on%20trading%20partners%2C%20stoking%20concerns%20that%20a%20global%20trade%20war%20may%20dampen%20demand%20for%20crude.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrent%20futures%20fell%20%241.97%2C%20or%202.63%25%2C%20to%20%2472.98%20a%20barrel%20by%200033%20GMT.%20U.S.%20West%20Texas%20Intermediate%20crude%20futures%20were%20down%20%241.98%2C%20or%202.76%25%2C%20to%20%2469.73.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOil%20Prices%20Fall%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOil%20prices%20fell%20to%20negative%20territory%20after%20rising%20by%20a%20dollar%20in%20post-settlement%20trade%20on%20Wednesday%20as%20Trump%20announced%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20on%20trading%20partners%2C%20stoking%20concerns%20that%20a%20global%20trade%20war%20may%20dampen%20demand%20for%20crude.%20Brent%20futures%20settled%2046%20cents%20higher%2C%20or%200.6%20per%20cent%2C%20at%20%2474.95%20a%20barrel%2C%20while%20U.S.%20West%20Texas%20Intermediate%20crude%20futures%20gained%2051%20cents%2C%20or%200.7%20per%20cent%2C%20to%20settle%20at%20%2471.71.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECurrencies%20Struggle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20rupee%20declined%20in%20the%20non-deliverable%20forward%20market%20on%20Thursday%20after%20Trump%20slapped%20a%2026%25%20tariff%20on%20imports%20from%20the%20Asian%20nation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201-month%20dollar%2Frupee%20non-deliverable%20forward%20was%20quoting%20at%2085.86-85.90%2C%20implying%20that%20the%20Indian%20currency%20is%20likely%20to%20open%2010-15%20paisa%20weaker%20when%20the%20onshore%20spot%20market%20opens%20at%209%3A00%20a.m.%20IST.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20offshore%20Chinese%20yuan%20dropped%20to%20a%20one-month%20low%20of%207.3482%20versus%20the%20U.S.%20dollar%2C%20before%20recovering%20marginally%20to%20a%20current%20rate%20of%207.32.%20The%20U.S.%20equity%20futures%20experienced%20a%20sizeable%20drop%2C%20and%20Japan%20led%20the%20broader%20Asian%20equity%20market%20lower.%C2%A0The%20dollar%20also%20slid%20broadly%20on%20Thursday%2C%20while%20the%20euro%20was%20steady.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20Tariffs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Trump%20on%20Wednesday%20unveiled%20a%20raft%20of%20punishing%20tariffs%20targeting%20countries%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20some%20of%20its%20closest%20trading%20partners%2C%20in%20a%20move%20that%20risks%20sparking%20a%20ruinous%20trade%20war.%20He%20announced%20a%20baseline%2010%20per%20cent%20tariff%20on%20imports%20and%20reserved%20some%20of%20the%20heaviest%20blows%20for%20what%20he%20called%20the%20%26quot%3Bnations%20that%20treat%20us%20badly%2C%26quot%3B%20including%2034%20percent%20on%20goods%20from%20superpower%20rival%20China%2C%2020%20percent%20on%20key%20ally%20the%20European%20Union%20and%2024%20percent%20on%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20China's%2034%20per%20cent%20tax%2C%20India%20got%20a%2026%20per%20cent%2C%20Vietnam%2046%20%C2%A0per%20cent%20and%20South%20Korea%2025%20%C2%A0per%20cent.%20The%20European%20Union%20was%20hit%20with%20a%2020%20%C2%A0per%20cent%20levy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20also%20shut%20a%20loophole%20used%20to%20ship%20low-value%20packages%20from%20China%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20hurt%20China's%20giant%20online%20retailers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%2078-year-old%20Republican%20--%20who%20held%20up%20a%20chart%20with%20a%20list%20of%20levies%20--%20said%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20kind%26quot%3B%20and%20so%20was%20only%20imposing%20half%20the%20amount%20that%20those%20countries%20taxed%20US%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrading%20partners%20are%20expected%20to%20respond%20with%20countermeasures%20of%20their%20own%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20dramatically%20higher%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20characterise%20this%20slate%20of%20tariffs%20as%20'worse%20than%20the%20worst%20case%20scenario'%20the%20Street%20was%20fearing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20analysts%20at%20Wedbush%2C%20with%20the%20technology%20supply%20chain%20in%20Taiwan%20and%20China%20hit%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EU.S.%20interest%20rate%20futures%20leapt%20as%20investors%20priced%20in%20slowing%20US%20growth%20and%20a%20higher%20chance%20of%20rate%20cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tariff%20rates%20unveiled%20this%20morning%20far%20exceed%20baseline%20expectations%2C%20and%20if%20they%20aren't%20negotiated%20down%20promptly%2C%20expectations%20for%20a%20recession%20in%20the%20US%20will%20rise%20dramatically%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20IG%20market%20analyst%20Tony%20Sycamore.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743643980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fnh8mmcvo_market-trump-tariffs_625x300_03_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fstocks-slump-gold-hits-new-high-as-markets-react-to-trumps-bombshell-tariffs-8073876%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stocks%20slumped%2C%20bonds%20surged%2C%20and%20gold%20hit%20a%20new%20high%20as%20markets%20braced%20for%20the%20impact%20of%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20sweeping%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Take%20a%20look%20inside%20Air%20Force%20Two%2C%20the%20155-foot%20custom%20jet%20plane%20vice%20presidents%20use%20to%20travel%20the%20world%