untries%2C%20would%20start%20paying%20the%20money%20necessary%20to%20run%20our%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20in%201929%20it%20all%20came%20to%20a%20very%20abrupt%20end%20with%20the%20Great%20Depression.%20And%20it%20would%20have%20never%20happened%20if%20they%20had%20stayed%20with%20the%20tariff%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%2C%20conveniently%20ignoring%20the%20multiple%20factors%20--%20including%20global%20economics%2C%20bank%20troubles%2C%20and%20the%20stock%20market%20crash%20--%20that%20led%20to%20the%20Great%20Depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20No%20surrender%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20highlighting%20tariffs%20on%20China%2C%20other%20Asian%20powers%20and%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20Trump%20turned%20his%20ire%20closer%20to%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20can%20no%20longer%20continue%20with%20the%20policy%20of%20unilateral%20economic%20surrender%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20pay%20the%20deficits%20of%20Canada%2C%20Mexico%20and%20so%20many%20other%20countries.%20We%20used%20to%20do%20it.%20We%20can't%20do%20it%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743641700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F2p0p15b_donald-trump_625x300_03_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fa-little-tough-love-top-quotes-from-donald-trump-tariff-talk-8073946%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20unveiled%20his%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariffs%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20sending%20fears%20of%20a%20trade%20war%20ricocheting%20around%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2