0deemed%20%26quot%3Bthe%20worst%20offenders%26quot%3B%20take%20effect%20at%2012%3A01am%20on%20April%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20steeper%20additional%20tariffs%20impact%20major%20US%20trading%20partners%2C%20with%20the%20European%20Union%20facing%20a%2020%20percent%20rate%20and%20China%20a%2034%20percent%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20China%2C%20the%20number%20stacks%20on%20an%20added%2020%20percent%20levy%20Trump%20imposed%20earlier%20this%20year%20over%20its%20alleged%20role%20in%20the%20supply%20chain%20of%20illicit%20fentanyl%2C%20taking%20the%20new%20additional%20figure%20to%2054%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20key%20partners%20include%20India%20with%20a%2026%20percent%20added%20rate%2C%20South%20Korea%20at%2025%20percent%20and%20Japan%20at%2024%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BFor%20nations%20that%20treat%20us%20badly%2C%20we%20will%20calculate%20the%20combined%20rate%20of%20all%20their%20tariffs%2C%20non-monetary%20barriers%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20cheating.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20numbers%2C%20he%20said%2C%20are%20%26quot%3Bapproximately%20half%20of%20what%20they%20are%20and%20have%20been%20charging%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Exclusions%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20US%20partners%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%2C%20however%2C%20are%20not%20subject%20to%20the%20new%20tariffs%2C%20White%20House%20officials%20said%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20earlier%20imposed%2025%20percent%20tariffs%20on%20imports%20from%20both%20countries%2C%20with%20a%20lower%20rate%20on%20Canadian%20energy%2C%20and%20they%20will%20continue%20to%20face%20these%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20goods%20entering%20the%20world's%20biggest%20economy%20under%20the%20US-Mexico-Canada%20Agreement%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20exempted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20reach%20deals%20on%20the%20levies%2C%20however%2C%20they%20will%20still%20come%20up%20against%20Trump's%20la