tly%20being%20negotiated%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20would%20be%20concluded%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%20as%20it%20would%20provide%20relief%20from%20these%20reciprocal%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20assess%20the%20impact%2C%20but%20looking%20at%20the%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20imposed%20on%20other%20countries%2C%20we%20are%20in%20a%20lower%20band.%20We%20are%20much%20better%20placed%20compared%20to%20our%20key%20competitors%20such%20as%20Vietnam%2C%20China%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20etc.%20We%20will%20definitely%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20tariffs%2C%20but%20we%20are%20much%20better%20placed%20than%20many%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20Sahai%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20President%20highlighted%20the%20high%20tariffs%20charged%20by%20India%20on%20American%20products%20as%20he%20announced%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20on%20countries%20worldwide%2C%20declaring%20a%2026%20per%20cent%20%26quot%3Bdiscounted%20reciprocal%20tariff%26quot%3B%20on%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20made%20the%20announcement%2C%20he%20held%20up%20a%20chart%20that%20showed%20the%20tariffs%20that%20countries%20like%20India%2C%20China%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20charge%2C%20along%20with%20the%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20these%20countries%20will%20now%20have%20to%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chart%20indicated%20that%20India%20imposed%2056%20per%20cent%20tariffs%2C%20%26quot%3Bincluding%20currency%20manipulation%20and%20trade%20barriers%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20America%20would%20now%20charge%20India%20a%20%26quot%3Bdiscounted%20reciprocal%20tariff%26quot%3B%20of%2026%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%2C%20very%2C%20very%20tough.%20Very%2C%20very%20tough.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20just%20left.%20He's%20a%20great%20friend%20of%20mine%2C%20but%20I%20said%2C%20'You're%20a%20friend%20of%20mine%2C%20but%20you're%20not%20treating%20us%20right.%20They%20charge%20us%2052%20per%20cent%E2%80%A6%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20s