%20announcing%20his%20country's%20%26quot%3Breciprocal%20tariffs%26quot%3B%20on%20those%20who%20tariff%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20recalled%20his%20brief%20remark%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20regarding%20trade%20ties%20with%20India%2C%20when%20the%20two%20leaders%20met%20in%20Washington%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou've%20not%20been%20treating%20us%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled%20as%20saying%20to%20PM%20Modi%2C%20when%20he%20spoke%20about%20India's%20high%20import%20duties.%20The%20US%20has%20now%20decided%20to%20reciprocate%20India's%20%26quot%3B52%20per%20cent%26quot%3B%20tariffs%20by%20charging%20Indian%20goods%20half%20of%20that%20-%2026%20per%20cent%2C%20when%20they%20are%20imported%20to%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20tariffs%20by%20New%20Delhi%20as%20%26quot%3Bvery%20very%20tough%26quot%3B%2C%20President%20Trump%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTheir%20Prime%20Minister%20(Narendra%20Modi)%20just%20left%20(US%20recently)...he%20is%20a%20great%20friend%20of%20mine%2C%20but%20I%20said%20to%20him%20that%20'you're%20a%20friend%20of%20mine%2C%20but%20you've%20not%20been%20treating%20us%20right'.%20India%20charges%20us%2052%20per%20cent%2C%20so%20we%20will%20charge%20them%20half%20of%20that%20-%2026%20per%20cent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E'PM%20Modi%20Is%20My%20Friend%20But...'%3A%20What%20Trump%20Said%20While%20Announcing%20India%20Tariff%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F1DTtajbU8L%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F1DTtajbU8L%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20NDTV%20(%40ndtv)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fndtv%2Fstatus%2F1907549675311231219%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%202%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20however%2C%20did%20not%20specify%20how%20these%20will%20be%20levied%2C%20or%20which%20industries%20would%20be%20impacted%20how%20much.%20The%20White%20House%20later%20said%20that%20country-specific%20tariffs%20will%20be%20over%20and%20above%20a%20%26quot%3Bbaseline%20tariff%26quot%3B%20of%2010%20per%20cent%20that%20the%20US%20has%20decided%20to%20charge%20on%20all%20goods%20that%20are%20imported%20into%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDue%20to%20a%20national%20emergency%20which%20has%20stemmed%20from%20security%20concerns%20due%20to%20persistent%20trade%20deficits%2C%20the%20US%20is%20imposing%20a%20baseline%2010%20per%20cent%20tariff%20that%20would%20start%20at%2012%3A01am%20local%20time%20(9%3A30%20am%20IST)%20on%20April%205%2C%20while%20the%20higher%20country-specific%20tariffs%20would%20begin%20from%2012%3A01%20am%20local%20time%20(9%3A30%20am%20IST)%20on%20April%209%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20himself%20%26quot%3Bkind%26quot%3B%2C%20President%20Trump%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20will%20charge%20other%20countries%20only%20half%20of%20what%20they%20charge%20us%26quot%3B.%20This%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bfair%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20his%20reciprocal%20tariff%20announcement%20from%20the%20White%20House%20Rose%20Garden%20as%20attendees%20cheered%20him%2C%20President%20Trump%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20far%20too%20long%2C%20other%20countries%20have%20looted%20and%20plundered%20us%2C%20while%20taking%20advantage%20of%20our%20policies.%20But%20no%20longer.%20April%202nd%20will%20forever%20be%20known%20as%20Liberation%20Day%20-%20when%20America%20reclaimed%20its%20industries.%20We%20will%20now%20impose%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20on%20countries%20that%20tariff%20us%20-%20Reciprocal%20means%20we%20do%20to%20them%2C%20what%20they%20do%20to%20us%2C%20as%20simple%20as%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20doing%20this%20we%20will%20reclaim%20our%20jobs%2C%20we%20will%20reclaim%20our%20industry%2C%20we%20will%20reclaim%20our%20small%20and%20medium%20scale%20businesses...and%20we%20will%20make%20America%20wealthy%20again.%20Jobs%20will%20come%20roaring%20into%20America%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20country-specific%20%26quot%3Bdiscounted%20reciprocal%20tariffs%26quot%3B%20include%20-%20China%20(34%20per%20cent)%2C%20European%20Union%20(20%20per%20cent)%2C%20Vietnam%20(46%20per%20cent)%2C%20Taiwan%20(32%20per%20cent)%2C%20Japan%20(24%20per%20cent)%2C%20India%20(26%20per%20cent)%2C%20United%20Kingdom%20(10%20per%20cent)%2C%20Bangladesh%20(37%20per%20cent)%2C%20Pakistan%20(29%20per%20cent)%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20(44%20per%20cent)%2C%20Israel%20(17%20per%20cent).%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743635220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-11%2F6kovt8c8_pm-modi-donald-trump-white-house-afp-file_625x300_01_November_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fyoure-a-friend-but-what-donald-trump-told-pm-narendra-modi-over-reciprocal-tariffs-8073526%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20announcing%20his%20country's%20%26quot%3Breciprocal%20tariffs%26quot%3B%20on%20those%20who%20tariff%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20recalled%20his%20brief%20remark%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20regarding%20trade%20ties%20with%20India%2C%20when%20the%20two%20leaders%20met%20in%20Washington%20recently.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fyoure-a-friend-but-what-donald-trump-told-pm-narendra-modi-over-reciprocal-tariffs-8073526%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Marine%20Le%20Pen's%20ban%20has%20outraged%20France's%20far%20right%20-%20and%20they%20may%20well%20seek%20revenge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743635196000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F3f13%2Flive%2F3997f390-0fcc-11f0-ac9f-c37d6fd89579.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles