ust-got-here-trump-distances-himself-from-soaring-egg-prices%2Farticleshow%2F119919947.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fi-just-got-here-trump-distances-himself-from-soaring-egg-prices%2Famp_articleshow%2F119919947.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fi-just-got-here-trump-distances-himself-from-soaring-egg-prices%2Famp_articleshow%2F119919947.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Stock%20Market%20Declines%20After%20Trump%20Unveils%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20Tariffs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20tariff%20offensive%20Donald%20Trump%20billed%20as%20key%20to%20America's%20long-term%20prosperity%20went%20down%20badly%20in%20markets%20late%20Wednesday%2C%20setting%20off%20declines%20of%202%25%20or%20more%20in%20equity%20benchmarks%20that%20had%20rallied%20for%20three%20days%20on%20hopes%20the%20program%20would%20be%20less%20draconian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%24577%20billion%20exchange-traded%20fund%20tracking%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20(SPY)%20fell%20about%202.5%25%20after%20the%20close%20of%20regular%20trading%2C%20wiping%20out%20an%20initial%20rally.%20Bonds%20climbed.%20Trump%20said%20Wednesday%20he%20will%20apply%20a%20minimum%2010%25%20tariff%20on%20all%20exporters%20to%20the%20US%20and%20slap%20additional%20duties%20on%20around%2060%20nations%20with%20the%20largest%20trade%20imbalances%20with%20the%20US.%20China%20will%20face%20a%2034%25%20rate%2C%20while%20the%20European%20Union%20will%20have%20a%2020%25%20levy%2C%20and%20Japan%20is%20seeing%20a%2024%25%20tariff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20late-session%20swoon%20halted%20three%20days%20of%20gains%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20as%20hopes%20were%20dashed%20the%20tariff%20program%20would%20be%20a%20lighter%20touch.%20Traders%20across%20asset%20classes%20now%20must%20brace%20for%20what%20promises%20to%20be%20a%20grueling%20stretch%20of%20trade%20negotiations%2C%20against%20an%20economic%20backdrop%20that%20has%20shown%20signs%20of%20softening%20as%20companies%20and%20consumers%20adjust%20to%20Trump's%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEye-watering%20tariffs%20on%20a%20country-by-country%20basis%20scream%20'negotiation%20tactic%2C'%20which%20will%20keep%20markets%20on%20edge%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Adam%20Hetts%20at%20Janus%20Henderson%20Investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20Steve%20Chiavarone%20at%20Federated%20Hermes%2C%20if%20Wednesday's%20announcement%20marks%20the%20most%20draconian%20levels%20of%20tariffs%2C%20and%20the%20news%20flow%20from%20here%20is%20about%20how%20countries%20are%20negotiating%20reductions%20to%20these%20rates%2C%20that%20could%20be%20good%20for%20markets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20may%20create%20enough%20of%20a%20selloff%20over%20the%20next%20day%20or%20so%20that%20it%20creates%20a%20buying%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWorst%20case%20scenario%20today%20would've%20been%20a%20low%20rate%20with%20threats%20of%20escalation.%20I'd%20rather%2C%20at%20this%20point%2C%20have%20higher%20rates%20with%20the%20potential%20to%20deescalate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20rose%200.7%25%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20Nasdaq%20100%20added%200.7%25.%20The%20Dow%20Jones%20Industrial%20Average%20gained%200.6%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%2010-year%20yield%20retreated%20four%20basis%20points%20to%204.13%25.%20The%20dollar%20fell%200.2%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20should%20slow%20trade%20and%20raise%20prices%2C%20squeezing%20profit%20margins%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Michael%20O'Rourke%20at%20JonesTrading%20Institutional%20Services.%20%26quot%3BThis%20will%20further%20slow%20a%20decelerating%20economy%20as%20it%20creates%20friction%20and%20distortion%20in%20global%20trade.%20I%20think%20we%20need%20to%20expect%20retaliation%2C%20which%20will%20likely%20lead%20to%20further%20escalation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUS%20import%20tariffs%20threaten%20to%20intensify%20the%20economic%20slowing%2C%20as%20well%20as%20add%20to%20inflationary%20pressures%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Todd%20Jablonski%20at%20Principal%20Asset%20Management.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20suggests%20markets%20may%20have%20already%20priced%20in%20these%20impacts.%20The%20Fed%20could%20act%20as%20a%20tailwind%20for%20markets%20if%20rate%20cuts%20are%20implemented%20in%20response%20to%20economic%20softness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20Chris%20Zaccarelli%20at%20Northlight%20Asset%20Management%2C%20markets%20are%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20struggle%20with%20the%20speed%20at%20which%20tariff%20details%20change%20as%20well%20as%20the%20ultimate%20result%20of%20the%20tariffs%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20silver%20lining%20for%20investors%20could%20be%20that%20this%20is%20only%20a%20starting%20point%20for%20negotiations%20with%20other%20countries%20and%20ultimately%20tariff%20rates%20will%20come%20down%20across%20the%20board%20-%20but%20for%20now%2C%20traders%20are%20shooting%20first%20and%20asking%20questions%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743632400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fci1b1d_us-stock-market-bloomberg_625x300_03_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-stock-market-declines-after-trump-announces-trade-tariffs-trump-tariff-announcement-us-tariffs-8073461%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20tariff%20offensive%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20billed%20as%20key%20to%20America's%20long-term%20prosperity%20went%20down%20badly%20in%20markets%2C%20setting%20off%20declines%20of%202%25%20or%20more%20in%20equity%20benchmarks%20t