%3EThe%20President%20also%20announced%20a%2020%20per%20cent%20levy%20on%20imports%20from%20the%20European%20Union%20and%2010%20per%20cent%20from%20the%20UK%20-%20two%20of%20the%20main%20trade%20partners%20and%20allies%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20On%20Japan%20too%2C%20he%20levied%20a%2024%20per%20cent%20tariff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20tariffs%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said%2C%20come%20over%20and%20above%20a%2010%20per%20cent%20base%20import%20duty%20on%20all%20products%20imported%20into%20the%20United%20States.%20President%20Trump%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20explain%20how%20these%20tariffs%20would%20be%20levied%20in%20an%20industry-wise%20break-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-announces-he-is-signing-order-imposing-reciprocal-tariffs-on-countries-worldwide-8073065%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannouncement%20was%20made%20to%20loud%20cheers%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20White%20House%20Rose%20Garden%2C%20as%20Donald%20Trump%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20far%20too%20long%2C%20other%20countries%20have%20looted%20and%20plundered%20us%2C%20while%20taking%20advantage%20of%20our%20policies.%20But%20no%20longer.%20April%202nd%20will%20forever%20be%20known%20as%20Liberation%20Day%20-%20when%20America%20reclaimed%20its%20industries.%20We%20will%20now%20impose%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20on%20countries%20that%20tariff%20us%20-%20Reciprocal%20means%20we%20do%20to%20them%2C%20what%20they%20do%20to%20us%2C%20as%20simple%20as%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20doing%20this%20we%20will%20reclaim%20our%20jobs%2C%20we%20will%20reclaim%20our%20industry%2C%20we%20will%20reclaim%20our%20small%20and%20medium%20scale%20businesses...and%20we%20will%20make%20America%20wealthy%20again.%20Jobs%20will%20come%20roaring%20into%20America%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20told%20reporters%20shortly%20after%20the%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariff%20announcement%20that%20due%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bnational%20emergency%26quot%3B%20which%20has%20stemmed%20from%20security%20concerns%20due%20to%20persistent%20trade%20deficits%2C%20the%20US%20is%20imposing%20a%20%26quot%3Bbaseline%26quot%3B%2010%20per%20cent%20tariff%20that%20would%20start%20at%2012%3A01am%20local%20time%20(9%3A30%20am%20IST)%20on%20April%205%2C%20while%20the%20higher%20country-specific%20tariffs%20would%20begin%20from%2012%3A01%20am%20local%20time%20(9%3A30%20am%20IST)%20on%20April%209.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743631980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F5h5bn5sc_donald-trump-tariffs-announcement-afp_625x300_03_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-announces-26-tariff-on-india-34-levy-on-chinese-imports-8073119%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20Wednesday%20announced%20huge%20new%20tariffs%20of%2034%20percent%20on%20imports%20from%20China%20and%2020%20percent%20on%20imports%20from%20the%20European%20Union%20--%20two%20of%20the%20main%20US%20trade%20partners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meghan%20Markle%20silences%20critics%20after%20As%20Ever%20sells%20out%20in%20an%20hour%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225201%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meghan%20Markle%20in%20September%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ed4cc4b8b41a9673fc674c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223901%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeghan%20Markle%20in%20September%202023.%3Cp%3ERolf%20Vennenbernd%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMeghan%20Markle's%20first%20As%20Ever%20collection%20sold%20out%20within%20an%20hour%20of%20its%20launch.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Duchess%20of%20Sussex's%20show%20%26quot%3BWith%20Love%