0at%20the%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariff%20announcement%20from%20the%20White%20House%20Rose%20Garden%2C%20President%20Trump%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20far%20too%20long%2C%20other%20countries%20have%20looted%20and%20plundered%20us%2C%20while%20taking%20advantage%20of%20our%20policies.%20But%20no%20longer.%20April%202nd%20will%20forever%20be%20known%20as%20Liberation%20Day%20-%20when%20America%20reclaimed%20its%20industries.%20We%20will%20now%20impose%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20on%20countries%20that%20tariff%20us%20-%20Reciprocal%20means%20we%20do%20to%20them%2C%20what%20they%20do%20to%20us%2C%20as%20simple%20as%20that.%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20doing%20this%20we%20will%20reclaim%20our%20jobs%2C%20we%20will%20reclaim%20our%20industry%2C%20we%20will%20reclaim%20our%20small%20and%20medium%20scale%20businesses...and%20we%20will%20make%20America%20wealthy%20again.%20Jobs%20will%20come%20roaring%20into%20America%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20will%20be%20kind%20on%20other%20nations%20and%20charge%20only%20half%20of%20what%20they%20charge.%26quot%3B%20He%20announced%20this%20showing%20a%20comparitive%20chart%20of%20tariffs%20-%20US%20vs%20Other%20Countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20was%20made%20shortly%20after%204pm%20local%20time%20(8pm%20GMT%20-%201%3A30am%20IST).%20There%20were%20loud%20cheers%20from%20the%20attendees%2C%20as%20President%20Trump%20was%20announcing%20the%20country-specific%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EDonald%20Trump's%20'trade%20war'%2C%20perhaps%20a%20more%20accurate%20term%20to%20describe%20the%20US%20legislation%2C%20will%20most%20certainly%20draw%20global%20retaliation.%20%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20the%20sectors%20which%20will%20be%20impacted%20most%20by%20American%20import%20duties%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20Steel%20and%20Aluminum%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20increased%20tariffs%20on%20all%20steel%20and%20aluminum%20imports%20to%2025%20per%20cent%2C%20and%20extended%20the%20duties%20to%20hundreds%20of%20downstream%20products.%20The%20US%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20aluminum%20importer%20and%20the%20second-largest%20steel%20importer.%20More%20than%20half%20of%20those%20volumes%20come%20from%20Canada%2C%20Mexico%20and%20Brazil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2)%20Automobiles%20and%20Motorbikes%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E-%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20announced%2025%20per%20cent%20'global'%20tariff%20on%20all%20imported%20cars%20and%20light%20trucks.%20The%20import%20duty%2C%20he%20said%2C%20will%20be%20imposed%20over%20and%20above%20previous%20duties%20on%20imports%20of%20finished%20vehicles.%20%26quot%3BOn%20motorbikes%2C%20Vitenam%20and%20India%20charge%20as%20much%20as%2070%20and%20100%20per%20cent%20respectively%2C%20and%20now%20we%20will%20do%20the%20same.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3)%20Pharmaceuticals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20decided%20that%20the%20US%20will%20tariff%20pharmaceutical%20raw%20materials%2C%20supplies%2C%20and%20medicines.%20This%20is%20a%20major%20change%20is%20US%20trade%20policy%20as%20pharmaceuticals%20have%20generally%20always%20been%20exempt%20from%20tariffs%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4)%20Alcohol%20and%20Alcobev%20Industry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20Donald%20Trump%20had%20announced%20a%20200%20per%20cent%20tariff%20on%20all%20wines%2C%20cognac%2C%20spirits%2C%20and%20other%20alcohol%20imports%20from%20Europe.%20This%20is%20in%20response%20to%20an%20EU%20plan%20to%20impose%20tariffs%20on%20American%20whiskey%20and%20other%20products.%20Whether%20or%20not%20this%20has%20been%20implemented%20in%20today's%20tariff%20structure%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5)%20Semiconductors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20President%20Trump%20said%20that%20tariffs%20on%20semiconductor%20chips%20would%20start%20at%20%26quot%3B25%20per%20cent%2C%20or%20higher.%26quot%3B%20This%2C%20he%20added%2C%20would%20rise%20substantially%20over%20the%20course%20of%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6)%20Agriculture%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E-%20The%20Trump%20Administration%20has%20said%20that%20it%20will%20reciprocate%20tariffs%20on%20agricultural%20and%20dairy%20produce%20on%20nations%20which%20tariff%20American%20agri%20products.%20Countries%20like%20India%2C%20which%20charges%20100%20per%20cent%20import%20duty%20on%20agricultural%20products%2C%20Japan%2C%20which%20charges%20700%20per%20cent%20on%20imported%20rice%2C%20China%20charges%2065%20per%20cent%2C%20and%20the%20EU%2C%20which%20charges%2050%20per%20cent%20on%20dairy%20products%20from%20the%20US%20must%20brace%20for%20reciprocal%20tariffs%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7)%20Meat%20Products%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20On%20beef%20imports%2C%20especially%20from%20Australia%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20banned%20beef%20imports%20from%20the%20US%20to%20protect%20their%20farmers.%20I%20can%20understand%20that%2C%20but%20why%20should%20we%20continue%20to%20import%20beef%20from%20them%20either.%20We%20have%20farmers%20too.%20So%2C%20effective%20midnight%2C%20we%20end%20all%20beef%20imports%20from%20Australia.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20duties%2C%20which%20are%20significant%2C%20and%20would%20impact%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20countries%2C%20including%20close%20allies%20of%20the%20US%2C%20have%20undone%20decades-old%20trade%20arrangements%20-%20some%20of%20which%20have%20been%20in%20place%20since%201947.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-announces-26-tariff-on-india-34-levy-on-chinese-imports-8073119%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecountry-specific%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20President%20Trump%20announced%20are%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EChina%20-%2034%20per%20cent%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndia%20-%2026%20per%20cent%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E