.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-meta-executive-sarah-wynn-williams-interview-careless-people-book-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ememoir%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BCareless%20People%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20catalyst%20for%20a%20probe%20into%20Meta's%20dealings%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20Hawley's%20post%2C%20Ravi%20Naik%2C%20the%20legal%20counsel%20for%20Wynn-Williams%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20his%20client%20is%20barred%20from%20speaking%20to%20lawmakers%20as%20a%20fallout%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eof%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-legal-win-bars-former-exec-promoting-book-careless-people-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemergency%20arbitration%20ruling%20Meta%20obtained%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month.%20The%20ruling%20enforces%20a%20non-disparagement%20clause%20in%20Wynn-Williams'%20severance%20agreement%20and%20bars%20her%20from%20promoting%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20they%20expect%20to%20be%20able%20to%20communicate%20with%20Ms.%20Wynn-Williams%2C%20and%20my%20client%20wishes%20to%20do%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20Naik%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BMeta%20has%2C%20however%2C%20silenced%20Ms.%20Wynn-Williams%20through%20an%20arbitration%20process%2C%20which%20means%20that%20she%20is%20prohibited%20from%20communicating%20with%20Congress.%20Ms.%20Wynn-Williams%20believes%20that%20people%20deserve%20to%20know%20the%20truth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBig%20News%20%E2%80%94%20Facebook%20whistleblower%20Sarah%20Wynn-Williams%20will%20testify%20NEXT%20WEEK%20in%20public%2C%20under%20oath%2C%20before%20my%20judiciary%20subcommittee%20re%3A%20her