0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F322755%2Fkarnataka-divaa-uthkarsha-project-surya-type-one-diabetes-awareness-for-underprivileged-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EType%201%20diabetes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20findings%2C%20however%2C%20are%20based%20on%20observational%20studies%2C%20and%20more%20research%20is%20needed%20to%20draw%20definitive%20conclusions.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20current%20evidence%20suggests%20that%20A2%20milk%20is%20less%20likely%20to%20cause%20gastrointestinal%20issues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20expert%2C%20Dr%20Pronobesh%2C%20an%20obstetrician%20and%20gynaecologist%20based%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CA2%20milk%20is%20a%20superior%20choice%20for%20gut%20health%20because%20the%20A2%20beta-casein%20is%20gentler%20on%20the%20digestive%20system.%20It%20reduces%20discomfort%20like%20bloating%2C%20gas%2C%20and%20inflammation%20in%20people%20who%20can%E2%80%99t%20tolerate%20normal%20milk.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20farm%20(Deep%20Roots%20Farms%20in%20Indore)%20where%20I%20get%20my%20A2%20milk%20feeds%20organic%20produce%20to%20their%20Gir%20cows%2C%20ensuring%20it%E2%80%99s%20safe.%20The%20cows%20are%20not%20hormonally%20altered%20to%20produce%20more%20milk%20and%20are%20treated%20with%20the%20utmost%20care%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20fresh%20A2%20milk%20to%20perfect%20yoghurt%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20making%20Jogurt%20is%20both%20intricate%20and%20time-consuming.%20The%20process%20begins%20by%20sourcing%20fresh%20A2%20milk%2C%20which%20is%20pasteurised.%20It%20is%20a%20process%20of%20heating%20milk%20to%20a%20specific%20temperature%20to%20kill%20harmful%20bacteria%20and%20pathogens.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20pasteurisation%2C%20I%20heat%20the%20milk%20to%2085%C2%B0C%20and%20then%20cool%20it%20down%20to%2045%C2%B0C.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20we%20add%